# TASK_PACKET

Task ID
CRUSHR-HARDEN-03C

Title
Typed comparison contracts and schema-backed experiment outputs

Role
BUILDER

Objective
Replace fragile untyped comparison/report surfaces with typed internal structures and schema-backed emitted artifacts for the comparison pipeline.

This packet exists because comparison artifacts currently rely too heavily on loosely structured JSON/value plumbing, which makes experiment outputs difficult to trust, evolve, and review.

This is a typed-contract packet.
It is not yet the decomposition packet.

